While the Ekiti guber election was going on, the EFCC arrested a party agent carrying a sack of money to induce buyers.
According to reports, the suspect is  an agent of the ruling APC.
He was taken into custody at Ola Oluwa Grammar School on Ilawe Road, Ado Ekiti.
Since the preparation for the 2023 general election started, candidates and contestants have prioritized vote-buying, committing cash and hard currencies to influencing delegates and voters.
